Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Municipality of Cagayan De Sulu in the Province of Tawi-Tawi to Cagayan De Tawi-Tawi
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 647
An Act Changing the Name of the Municipality of Cagayan De Sulu in the Province of Tawi-Tawi to Cagayan De Tawi-Tawi
Section 1. The name of the Municipality of Cagayan de Sulu in the Province of Tawi-Tawi is changed to Cagayan de Tawi-Tawi.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
